{"tid":1476382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家應該先搞清楚616係想擠提定衝擊聯繫匯率","createTime":"2019-08-15T19:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T20:31:24.000Z","uid":29514,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8f8f5adeebe52f44a6e2550044f787fe06f789","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:54:09.000Z","msg":"前者容易好多，因為銀行大部分錢都借左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係剩返好少%既現金比人提款。而後者就難好多金管局聲稱有4000億外匯儲備，我當有3000億比支共偷左，而剩返既1000億都遠遠多過銀行既存款儲備金，所以如果係要衝擊聯繫匯率既話難度係高好多，就算李嘉誠將所有錢轉曬美金都破壞唔到聯繫匯率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />李嘉誠身家都無1000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要香港頭幾大富豪都一齊做先有d機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返616既行動，而家有d巴打話想擠提，有d就話想轉曬做美金安全d, 但係轉美金同擠提係有矛盾。例子：A巴打係銀行拎左十萬港幣，之後將呢十萬港幣轉做美金，咁呢十萬港幣就會入返去銀行既存款儲備金，姐係銀行既港幣現金係無少到架，只要聯繫匯率唔被破壞，對經濟係0影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果我地全部人剩係提取港幣而唔轉任何外幣，銀行既存款儲備先會真正減少，當銀行唔夠港幣既時候就會擠提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我想講現階段單靠小市民既力量係唔可能衝擊聯繫匯率，如果真係想破壞香港經濟既不如剩係提款港幣唔轉任何外幣咁先可以令到銀行擠提，有人計過只要有60萬人同時間拎一萬港紙香港既所有銀行存款儲備就會清空，我相信擠提會容易過衝擊聯繫匯率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />616全民拎港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545345f4e7b9beb3d5cac04426fbf802ac6114ab","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:54:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"094b20585f4c724f5c57ca2ca0b7db7466fb41e4","tid":1476382,"uid":12773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:57:05.000Z","msg":"出年616？<br />\n816呀<br />\n時間日期都未識得分！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29779de684041743912bf7594e8e4a46ad7ef309","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:57:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc74413107e33e75a31c84eb624db9b3c3703e7","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094b20585f4c724f5c57ca2ca0b7db7466fb41e4","tid":1476382,"uid":12773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:57:05.000Z","msg":"出年616？<br />\n816呀<br />\n時間日期都未識得分！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:57:28.000Z","msg":"太眼訓打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148426314ce1bdfb831b5f26774b558088dfb5b6","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:57:55.000Z","msg":"仲要打錯2次自隊十打膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba85380648dc2f494c04a91c743fc812608a0c2","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:00:19.000Z","msg":"唔好執著我打錯日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下內文先"},{"pid":"b149efacdc43780e35771a524732db42ae2203c7","tid":1476382,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba85380648dc2f494c04a91c743fc812608a0c2","tid":1476382,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:00:19.000Z","msg":"唔好執著我打錯日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下內文先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:02:24.000Z","msg":"會唔會太遲先出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經有人換左美金"},{"pid":"ee127d3e478ce08